description:
The Gymnast is on a roll, and is shaping up to be one of the sites elite wrestlers. She is using her legs more and is starting to feel comfortable on the mat. The Gymnast has amazing strength in her legs and arms, enough to crush most wrestlers into submission, and she did, amassing 6 submissions against one of the hardest BSDM models on the net today.
Blondie is a tough never quit scraper. She is still learning and is getting better each match. Her determination to wrestle hard every second is unmatched by any.
title: The Gymnast (3-5) Ranked 8th Blondie(0-2) Ranked 11th
